{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅老先生","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"吴兄何必自谦太甚，方才吴兄虽自云学剑不成，想来武学上造诣必深，老夫虽对此道外行，却甚钦羡古侠士仗剑行义之风哩。","tone":"陈述","chapter":23,"line_start":2,"line_end":4},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"雕虫小技，难人法眼，今日吴某欣得知音，且舞一剑为先生卸除寒气。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":6,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":null,"text":"献丑！","tone":"陈述","chapter":23,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅老先生","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"吴先生方才施的三招真好看，可否再舞一遍让老朽仔细欣赏一下？","tone":"好奇","chapter":23,"line_start":30,"line_end":32},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅老先生","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"你那倒数第二招是否有点不对——","tone":"疑问","chapter":23,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"你是谁？","tone":"厉声","chapter":23,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅老先生","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"你是谁？","tone":"疑问","chapter":23,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"无极岛主无恨生！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"梅山民！你听过吗？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"原来你是梅山民，今日叫你——","tone":"冷酷","chapter":23,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"世外三仙不过尔尔，你那三招剑法中依然有毛病。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":23,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"你且说来看看。","tone":"疑问","chapter":23,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"我只要左面给你一记'韦护抡杵'，右面给你一记'丹阳渡苇'，就能逼你露出左面破绽。","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":76,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"我左面虽露破绽，可是脚下乃是'盘弓射雕'的势子，只要你一发招，我双脚马上踢你丹田要穴，用是左掌'横劈华山'，右指取你双目，你躲得了下就躲不了上。","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":82,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"若是我用我那'虬枝剑式'中的'寒梅吐蕊'，立刻就叫你不暇自保，只是'虬枝剑式'乃是我自己所创，说与你听你也不明白。","tone":"得意","chapter":23,"line_start":88,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":null,"text":"任他功力盖世，不过一介武夫耳。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":23,"line_start":98,"line_end":99}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_mei_shan_min","name":"梅山民","alias":["梅老先生","七妙神君"],"identity":"七妙神君，海内奇才，七艺冠绝海内","faction":"无门派","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"登峰造极","one_line":"海内七妙神君，七艺冠绝，功力尽失但武学仍有进无退","personality":{"traits":["嗜武如命","倔强自傲","奇才横溢","心思缜密","爱恨分明"],"speech_style":"时而温和时而傲慢","temperament":"偏激"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":["skill_qiu_zhi_jian_fa"],"rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":56,"line_end":56,"text":"梅山民！你听过吗？"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":70,"line_end":70,"text":"世外三仙不过尔尔"}]},{"id":"char_wu_hen_sheng","name":"无恨生","alias":["吴兄","无极岛主"],"identity":"世外三仙之一，无极岛主","faction":"无极岛","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"返璞归真","one_line":"世外三仙之一，无极岛主，文武双绝，驻颜不老","personality":{"traits":["自负甚高","文武双绝","嫉恶如仇","才智盖世","冷峻内敛"],"speech_style":"时而豪迈时而冷峻","temperament":"高傲"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":["skill_po_yu_quan_fa"],"rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":50,"line_end":50,"text":"无极岛主无恨生！"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_wu_ji_dao","name":"无极岛","type":"武林门派","location":"海外","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"世外三仙所在的海外仙岛","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":50,"line_end":50,"text":"无极岛主无恨生！"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_wu_ji_dao","name":"无极岛","region":"海外","one_line":"世外三仙所在的海外仙岛","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":50,"line_end":50,"text":"无极岛主无恨生！"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_mei_zi_xiang","name":"梅子香","type":"special","owner":"char_mei_shan_min","one_line":"本地特产梅酒","description":"用夹道的梅儿酿成的美酒，花香味渗入酒中，别有一股馥烈的味道","effects":[],"origin":"本地特产","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_mei_shan_min","char_wu_hen_sheng"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":226,"line_end":226,"text":"梅子香正是本地特产"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"论内功，你功力即使不失，怕也非我对手，但论剑术，则各人聪明才智不同，与功力关系较少，咱们以手代剑，以口代手，来个口上谈兵如何？啊，看你手上是壶陈年老酒，咱们就算煮酒论剑吧，也算得一桩雅事，哈哈。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":108,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"你这招华山神拳中的'自解金铃'固然论攻论守都有若铜墙铁壁，但遇上我的'虬枝剑法'可就不行了。","tone":"得意","chapter":23,"line_start":132,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":null,"text":"哼！这老家伙果然是名不虚传，毒辣得很！","tone":"冷酷","chapter":23,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":null,"text":"我无恨生岂可一再倚仗较高的功力取胜？","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":164,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"无恨生，你这招论攻可说锐利无比，但论守却得另择招式相助！","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":196,"line_end":198},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"请教。","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"id":"skill_qiu_zhi_jian_fa","name":"虬枝剑法","type":"剑法","faction":"无门派","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"梅山民独创的剑法，以梅枝为剑，招式精妙","techniques":[{"id":"tech_han_mei_tui_rui","name":"寒梅吐蕊","type":"attack","description":"全攻势子，一圈再吐封住对手攻势再点指"},{"id":"tech_leng_mei_fu_mian","name":"冷梅拂面","type":"attack","description":"斜掠而上如梅枝横出"},{"id":"tech_zha_jing_mei_duo","name":"乍惊梅多","type":"attack","description":"双掌一翻一压遍袭敌手大穴"}],"progression":["梅山民独创"],"effects":["克制中原各派招式"],"combat_style":"以巧破力，连环杀招","rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":132,"line_end":134,"text":"遇上我的'虬枝剑法'可就不行了"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":170,"line_end":170,"text":"正是'乍惊梅多'的招式"}]},{"id":"skill_po_yu_quan_fa","name":"破玉拳法","type":"掌法","faction":"无极岛","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"无极岛绝学，以剑招递出威力奇大","techniques":[{"id":"tech_po_yu_zhang_fa","name":"破玉掌法","type":"attack","description":"无极岛绝学攻守兼备"}],"progression":["无极岛传承"],"effects":["威力大得出奇"],"combat_style":"先守后攻，一鸣惊人","rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":188,"line_end":188,"text":"正是无极岛的绝学——'破玉拳法'"}]}],"techniques":[{"id":"tech_han_mei_tui_rui","name":"寒梅吐蕊","type":"attack","source_skill":"skill_qiu_zhi_jian_fa","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":120,"line_end":122,"text":"正是'虬枝掌式'中的'寒梅吐蕊'"}]},{"id":"tech_leng_mei_fu_mian","name":"冷梅拂面","type":"attack","source_skill":"skill_qiu_zhi_jian_fa","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":136,"line_end":136,"text":"正是绝学'冷梅拂面'！"}]},{"id":"tech_zha_jing_mei_duo","name":"乍惊梅多","type":"attack","source_skill":"skill_qiu_zhi_jian_fa","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":170,"line_end":172,"text":"正是'乍惊梅多'的招式"}]},{"id":"tech_zi_jie_jin_ling","name":"自解金铃","type":"attack","source_skill":"skill_hua_shan_shen_quan","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":132,"line_end":132,"text":"华山神拳中的'自解金铃'"}]},{"id":"tech_shuang_zhuang_zhang","name":"双撞掌","type":"attack","source_skill":null,"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":156,"line_end":156,"text":"刚想施出'双撞掌'"}]},{"id":"tech_pai_tui_du","name":"拍腿肚","type":"attack","source_skill":null,"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":160,"line_end":160,"text":"'拍腿肚'乃是太极门中的招式"}]},{"id":"tech_jin_gang_zhi","name":"金刚指","type":"attack","source_skill":null,"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":150,"line_end":150,"text":"夹着'金刚指'功"}]}],"factions":[{"id":"faction_hua_shan_pai","name":"华山派","type":"武林门派","location":"中原","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"中原武林门派，有华山神拳等绝学","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":132,"line_end":132,"text":"华山神拳中的'自解金铃'"}]},{"id":"faction_tai_ji_men","name":"太极门","type":"武林门派","location":"中原","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"中原武林门派，以'黏'字诀著称","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":160,"line_end":160,"text":"'拍腿肚'乃是太极门中的招式"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_xiao_ji_dao","name":"小戢岛","region":"海外","one_line":"世外三仙之首平凡上人所在","source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":184,"line_end":184,"text":"小戢岛上和世外三仙之首平凡上人过招"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_mei_shan_min","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":56,"line_end":56,"text":"梅山民！你听过吗？"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":70,"line_end":70,"text":"世外三仙不过尔尔"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":132,"line_end":134,"text":"遇上我的'虬枝剑法'可就不行了"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_wu_hen_sheng","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":50,"line_end":50,"text":"无极岛主无恨生！"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":108,"line_end":112,"text":"煮酒论剑"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":152,"line_end":152,"text":"哼！这老家伙果然是名不虚传"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_mei_shan_min","type":"对手","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"惺惺相惜"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"酒温好啦——","tone":"陈述","chapter":23,"line_start":202,"line_end":202},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"咱们还是先尝尝这美酒吧！","tone":"温柔","chapter":23,"line_start":204,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"荒山野地，没有器具，权且以此代杯，向老先生索讨美酒一杯！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":208,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"好说！好说！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":23,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"阁下刚才那招绝学，上盘好像是虚式，下盘却踩七星，随机可变为八卦之方位，敌手如果不察，先让上盘，你必立变下盘的七星位至八卦，然后用'连环脚'袭敌，再转上三路的虚式为实，攻势变化不可说不多——","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"不敢问什么招式可以破解？","tone":"疑问","chapter":23,"line_start":232,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"我不踩你上盘的攻势，下盘顺着你由七星变为八卦的式子踢出数脚，再等你上盘转虚为实之际，'力斩蓝关'的式子打你胁下'章门'、'紫鸩'，你就不暇自保——","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"且慢，我在你下盘踢出'连环脚'时，立即变上盘，用太极'黏'字诀化开——","tone":"焦急","chapter":23,"line_start":240,"line_end":240},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":null,"text":"我无恨生自以为一代奇人，但若不是那千年朱果，看来这鬼才的功力可要和我不相上下，而招式之奇似还有过之哩！最难得的便是这家伙不但武学通神，而且文才、棋艺，好像每一样都凌驾于我之上哩？哼！可惜，这等人才竟会是一个大大的淫贼——","tone":"无奈","chapter":23,"line_start":250,"line_end":254},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"暂且住手，我有一事相请。","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":264,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_mei_shan_min","speaker_name":"梅山民","listener":"char_wu_hen_sheng","text":"好说！老夫不敢当！","tone":"认真","chapter":23,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"你知道缪九娘吗？","tone":"厉声","chapter":23,"line_start":270,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"你这老贼，万死不得赎其罪，你有没有天良？害得她活活疯癫而死！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":23,"line_start":274,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_wu_hen_sheng","speaker_name":"无恨生","listener":"char_mei_shan_min","text":"狂贼啊狂贼，亏你满腹奇才，竟不自检点，我无恨生说不得今日要替天行道！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":23,"line_start":296,"line_end":298}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_miao_jiu_niang","name":"缪九娘","alias":[],"identity":"为七妙神君而死的女子","faction":"无门派","role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"为七妙神君而死的女子，死前疯癫","personality":{"traits":["痴情","凄苦","疯癫"],"speech_style":"无对话","temperament":"悲苦"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_mei_shan_min","type":"恋人","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"为他而死"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":270,"line_end":270,"text":"你知道缪九娘吗？"},{"chapter":23,"line_start":274,"line_end":276,"text":"害得她活活疯癫而死！"}]},{"id":"char_miao_qi_niang","name":"缪七娘","alias":[],"identity":"无恨生之妻","faction":"无门派","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"无恨生之妻","personality":{"traits":[],"speech_style":"无对话","temperament":"无"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_wu_hen_sheng","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"夫妻"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[23],"source_refs":[{"chapter":23,"line_start":104,"line_end":104,"text":"他曾笑对缪七娘道"}]},{"id":"char_ping_fan_shang_ren","name":"平凡上人","alias":[],"identity":"世外三仙之首","faction":"无极岛","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"返璞归真","one_line":"世外三仙之首，功力盖世","personality":{"traits":["武功盖世","世外高人"],"speech_style":"无对话","temperament":"高深莫测"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_wu_hen_sheng","type":"合作者","intensi